        <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.wheelofheaven.world/library/lets-welcome-the-extraterrestrials/">&lt;p&gt;This page displays &quot;Let&#x27;s Welcome the Extraterrestrials&quot; with interactive features for viewing the original French text alongside the published English translation.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The book contains 4 chapters: a wide-ranging Q&amp;amp;A addressing the most common questions raised after the first two messages, the new revelations Raël was permitted to share after a three-year waiting period, the framing of Raëlism as an atheist religion, and a collection of commentaries and testimonials from Raëlians.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
